363
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:51,710
Now that I think about it, I was too strict on him when he was young.

364
00:38:52,570 --> 00:38:54,970
After all, he was just a child.

365
00:38:56,010 --> 00:39:00,110
Even if I let him fool around a little or be a little mischievous,

366
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:02,460
