370
00:39:16,620 --> 00:39:19,140
I might really be getting old now.

371
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:25,180
Maybe, it's because I really want Chengyin to stay by my side.

372
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:33,090
I also don't know what's wrong lately. I keep on thinking about when Chengyin was young.

373
00:39:34,620 --> 00:39:38,600
Rongshuang, accompany me to the Eastern Palace.

374
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,090
Yes.

375
00:39:40,090 --> 00:39:43,640
Do you know that Grand Empress Dowager went to see a fortune teller yesterday?

376
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:46,430
She already picked out names for the little prince.

377
00:39:46,430 --> 00:39:48,300
What if it's a little princess though?

378
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:51,620
It's still better to prepare for it. The future is long.

379
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:58,340
Empress.

380
00:40:02,130 --> 00:40:04,740
Why are Crown Prince's clothes out here?

381
00:40:05,490 --> 00:40:10,350
